data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT OF OWNER. Don't miss the opportunity to call this beautiful, well maintained home yours. This two-story, spacious 4 bed, 2.5 bath Chadwick plan offers a dining/flex room with coffered ceilings, signature trimming and chandelier. The kitchen/breakfast area, overlooking the family room, is a great place to host friends and family. Features include, stainless steel appliances, espresso cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and LVT flooring throughout the lower level. The second floor features an owner's suite and bathroom with a separate shower/tub, double vanity and huge walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms with walk-in closets, one bathroom with double vanity and laundry room. Fenced backyard bolstering a peach and banana trees is a great place to sit back and relax. Conveniently located near the airport and 20 minutes from downtown Atlanta. This home is a must see and easy to show! Schedule your showing today! MOTIVATED Seller.
